<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email Verification</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f6f8;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 30px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            color: #365CCE;
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            color: #4a4a4a;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .token {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            background-color: #e9f1ff;
            color: #365CCE;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .note {
            color: #666666;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Email Verification</h1>
        <p>Dear {{email}},</p>
        <p>Thank you for registering with us. To complete your registration, please use the following one-time verification token:</p>
        <div class="token">{{token}}</div>
        <p>This token will expire shortly, so please use it as soon as possible. If you did not register with us, you may ignore this email.</p>
        <p class="note">Note: For your security, do not share this token with anyone.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
